author: nick
msg: TIKA-451 - Inconsistent date format for Metadata.CREATION_DATE and Metadata.LAST_MODIFIED
Make CREATION_DATE and LAST_MODIFIED Date property instances, and add support for getting and setting Dates (+getting ints), as discussed in TIKA-451
Unit tests for getting and settings ints and dates are included. Work to update the existing parsers to make use of the new Date setter is still outstanding
